awake.

00:04:37.090 --> 00:04:41.910
Among many other things, cortisol actually
increases the volume of the blood in your

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:47.440
body, which causes the blood vessels (including
the ones below your eyes) to engorge to accommodate

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:48.440
